snippet.title: PS4 / PS Vita 『Bullet Girls Phantasia』 Promotion Video
snippet.description:
Military training in another world! 『Bullet Girls Phantasia』 is coming to Korea, Japan, and Asia simultaneously on Aug 9, 2018!

The Cait Sith, Merrina Iris, appearing in 『Bullet Girls Phantasia』 (CV: Nozomi Yamamoto) introduces each game feature as a virtual YouTuber!
